# --- Heavy ML artifacts: keep new ones out of git (see MODELS.md) ---
# Run-time weights are published as GitHub Release assets and fetched via scripts/fetch-models.sh; 
# the training archive lives in bulk storage.
# TB event files + prediction .npz are deliberately TRACKED (small, source of
# truth for training curves + re-derivable analysis)
**/weights/*.pt
runtime/deployed/**/*.pt
